== 出道歷程 ==
該團體是[[松岡李那|松岡李那]]師弟，並在2015年出席[[香港書展|香港書展]]相關活動<ref>{{cite news|title=【書展開鑼】松岡李那師弟冇戴龍珠假髮 R-ice：要顧及形象|url=http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20150715/53975754|accessdate=2015-07-15|date=2016-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150717001822/http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20150715/53975754|archive-date=2015-07-17|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=R-ICE突襲書展派寫真|url=http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/entertainment/art/20150711/19215529|accessdate=2015-07-11|date=2016-04-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150714004311/http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/entertainment/art/20150711/19215529|archive-date=2015-07-14|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。2016年R-ICE（[[鄧佑剛|鄧佑剛]]、[[李礎業|李礎業]]、[[小林龍介|小林龍介]]）計畫發片出道時，團員小林龍介被發現曾在日本拍攝[[男同性戀色情片|男同性戀色情片]]，導致經紀公司將他一人解約<ref>{{cite news|title=小林竜介香港組團出道　拍GV暗黑口交照外流慘被解約！|url=http://star.ettoday.net/news/678477|accessdate=2016-04-11|date=2016-04-12|archive-date=2016-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160411175126/http://star.ettoday.net/news/678477|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=男星被騙拍GV 慘遭經紀公司開除|url=http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20160411006530-260404|accessdate=2016-04-11|date=2016-04-12|archive-date=2016-04-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160414153231/http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20160411006530-260404|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=拍GV曝光慘遭開除 日男星嘆當時被騙只賺__元|url=http://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/1661292|accessdate=2016-04-11|date=2016-04-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160412195414/http://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/1661292|archive-date=2016-04-12|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，該事件也使R-ICE臨時取消台灣的宣傳行程<ref>{{cite news|title=【獨家】摟400億大亨熱舞被作廢　辣模挑郎打槍蒟蒻男|url=http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170702/1152211/|publisher=蘋果日報|accessdate=2017-07-02|author=林丞偉|date=2017-07-12|archive-date=2017-07-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170702082432/http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170702/1152211/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同年，松岡李那與R-ICE（李礎業、鄧佑剛、[[陳獻略|陳獻略]]、{{link-ja|安田慎吾|安田慎吾}}）推出廣東歌曲《情迷》<ref>{{cite news|title=松岡專注工作否認戀林德信|url=http://www.singtao.ca/calgary/366771/2016-08-10/post-松岡專注工作否認戀林德信|publisher=星島日報|accessdate=2016-08-09|author=Jazz Chow|date=2016-08-16|language=zh-hant}}{{Dead link|date=2019年10月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。也與[[芹那|芹那]]、[[楊鎧凝|楊鎧凝]]、[[王友良|王友良]]共同出席《櫻桃小丸子30周年生日會香港站》的相關活動<ref>{{cite news|title=芹那爆自小愛剪小丸子髮型|url=http://toronto.singtao.ca/857911/2016-05-08/post-芹那爆自小愛剪小丸子髮型/?variant=zh-hk|accessdate=2016-05-08|date=2016-06-06}}{{Dead link|date=2019年11月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。

== 演藝歷程 ==
2017年R-ICE團員人數再次異動，改為雙人男子演唱團體（[[鄧佑剛|鄧佑剛]]和[[李礎業|李礎業]]）的形式繼續活動<ref>{{cite news|title=（專訪）男星拍同志色情片遭解約 前戰友透露他去向|publisher=自由時報|url=http://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/2079605|accessdate=2017-05-26|author=陽昕翰|date=2017-06-04|language=zh-hant|archive-date=2017-05-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170526004249/http://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/2079605|dead-url=no}}</ref>。另外，與[[松岡李那|松岡李那]]和[[王友良|王友良]]組成團體「'''[[LIR|LIR]]'''」<ref>{{cite news|title=女模曾沾歌王兒子 又被爆和金馬配角兒有曖昧？|publisher=自由時報|url=http://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/2062502|date=2017-05-09|author=蔡琛儀|accessdate=2017-05-16|language=zh-hant|archive-date=2017-05-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170512235438/http://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/2062502|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=櫻桃小丸子班底發片 魏蔓端苦瓜鼓勵|publisher=大紀元|url=http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/17/5/9/n9123546.htm|date=2017-05-09|author=鄭宜芬|accessdate=2017-05-16|language=zh-hant|archive-date=2017-05-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170521131836/http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/17/5/9/n9123546.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=LIR全裸拍MV|publisher=中國時報|url=http://www.chinatimes.com/newspapers/20170510000609-260112|date=2017-05-10|author=黃保慧|accessdate=2017-05-16|language=zh-hant|archive-date=2017-05-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170513171546/http://www.chinatimes.com/newspapers/20170510000609-260112|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=魏蔓餵食蜜苦瓜 挺LIR樂壇發光|publisher=自由時報|url=http://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/paper/1100930|date=2017-05-10|author=陳慧玲|accessdate=2017-05-16|language=zh-hant|archive-date=2017-05-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170513073108/http://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/paper/1100930|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

